A multi-tool learning instance contains:
(i) a query/task $q Q $;
(ii) an interactive environment with latent state $s_t S $ and observation $o_t O $ at step $t$;
(iii) a tool inventory $ D =\ d_i\ _ i=1 ^ N $, where each tool $d$ is described by a schema/signature $ _d$
(e.g., name, description, constraints, return format).
